GDML Processor for Geant4 setup and build instructions
======================================================

Requirements
------------
Build Geant4 with shared libraries support enbled, e.g.:

export G4LIB_BUILD_SHARED=1


Unpacking
---------

cd $G4INSTALL/examples/advanced
tar zvxf /path/to/gdml.tgz

Xerces-C XML Parser
-------------------

Set the environment variable XERCESCROOT:

export XERCESROOT=$G4INSTALL/examples/advanced/gdml/xerces-c

Build GDML Processor
--------------------

cd $G4INSTALL/examples/advanced/gdml
gmake

Run sample application
----------------------

Set LD_LIBRARY_PATH to the location of the G4 shared libraries + Xerces-C libraries:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$G4LIB/$G4SYSTEM:$XERCESCROOT/lib:.

cd $G4INSTALL/examples/advanced/gdml/sample
$G4WORKDIR/bin/$G4SYSTEM/gogdml

